.TH ST_NUPR 3 "13 Nov 2005" "Karma Distribution"
.SH FUNCTION
st_nupr \- Convert a string to uppercase, up to a specified length.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <karma_st.h>
.sp
.B char * st_nupr
.sp
(char *string, int str_len)
.SH DESCRIPTION
Convert a string to uppercase, up to a specified length.
.IP \fIstring\fP 1i
The string.
.IP \fIstr_len\fP 1i
The maximum number of characters to convert.
.SH RETURN VALUE
The address of the string.
.SH Multi-threading Level
Unsafe.
